Responsibilities

  Assist Construction Manager to oversee the Quality Control of the site and ensure all subcontractors are meeting the project's quality specification
  Help to administer Quality procedure at site and manageing quality work performed by contractors
  Responsible in ensuring project is constructed, tested, inspected and documented in accordance to project specifications


Requirements

  Degree in Mechanical Engineering&nbsp;
  Min. 10 years experience in similar role in the oil &amp; gas industry, preferably onshore refinery / petrochemical projects
  Willing to be based in Jurong Island
  Willing to take on 2-3 years contract
